These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
House: wooden, futuristic, colonial
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the wooden house is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the futuristic house##1
4. the colonial house is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| House   | colonial | wooden | futuristic |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, golf
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Sport   | golf    | swimming     | skiing        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, orange, aquamarine
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Color   | orange | apricot     | aquamarine  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker
1. the person watching sports movies is the doctor##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the social-worker##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Job         | bartender  | doctor | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
City: berlin, paris, colone
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to berlin and the canadian##2
2. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| City         | berlin   | colone | paris    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, december
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| Birthday   | december     | february    | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk, techno
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the owner of the turtle and the fan of techno##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop | funk |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
