3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the project-manager##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Job   | videographer | freelancer | project-manager |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

