.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, epic, romance
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | epic  | western  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

