.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
There are 3 different nationalities: french, american, turkish
1. the french is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the turkish is in an even position##4
3. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Nationality       | american | turkish | french   |

