.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, teacher
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, azalea
1. the teacher is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the journalist##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | teacher | journalist |
| Flower   | aconite | azalea   | sunflower |

