.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, mauve, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the french##1
2. the person who likes red is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
