.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, musician, journalist
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the journalist is between the musician and the owner of the pony##2
2. the musician is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Job   | musician | journalist | mechanic |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

