.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, romance, spy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | spy     | romance |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | badminton | swimming    |

