.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, country, disco
1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
4. the fan of country is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | hamster  | turtle   | guinea-pig |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country | r&b       |

 